# 7. 雷鳴の夜

Little Mafuyu: Eep...!
Little Mafuyu: (That thunder's getting louder...)
Little Mafuyu: ...!
Little Mafuyu: *Whimper* (I'm so scared...)
Little Mafuyu: Mommy...
Little Mafuyu: (I wanna be with her...)
Little Mafuyu: (But she said I'm a big girl now, so I'm supposed to sleep by myself...)
Little Mafuyu: (Still...)
Little Mafuyu: ...! *Sob*
Little Mafuyu: I'm really scared...
Little Mafuyu: Mommy...
Mafuyu's Father: Mafuyu?
Mafuyu's Father: Are you asleep...?
Little Mafuyu: Daddy...?
Mafuyu's Father: Huh...?
Mafuyu's Father: Mafuyu...! You're awake?
Little Mafuyu: *Sob* I-I'm sorry...
Little Mafuyu: ...!
Little Mafuyu: *Cry*
Mafuyu's Father: Mafuyu...!
Mafuyu's Father: Are you having trouble falling asleep...?
Little Mafuyu: I-I'm sorry...
Little Mafuyu: But that thunder's so loud, and I'm really scared...
Mafuyu's Father: I had no idea... I'm sorry for not noticing sooner.
Mafuyu's Father: It's okay, honey. I'll stay right here until you fall asleep.
Little Mafuyu: Oh...
Little Mafuyu: B-But Mommy said I'm supposed to sleep by myself now...
Mafuyu's Father: Don't worry. I'll tell her that you went to sleep all on your own.
Little Mafuyu: You will...?
Mafuyu's Father: Yes, so it's okay.
Mafuyu's Father: Here, I'll hold your hand like this. See? That thunder isn't so scary, right?
Little Mafuyu: *Nod*
Little Mafuyu: Oh...
Little Mafuyu: (Daddy's hand is so warm... I feel a lot better now.)
Little Mafuyu: (Because I know he's here with me...)
Mafuyu: To me, my dad...
Mafuyu: I don't remember very clearly...
Mafuyu: But I think I was able to fall asleep because he made me safe by holding my hand.
Rin: <Really...?>
Rin: <Then, I think it's okay for you to trust him...>
Mafuyu: What...?
Rin: <That story you just told me...>
Rin: <It proved that you have some good memories about your dad...>
Mafuyu: Oh...
Rin: <I can't guarantee anything just based on that...>
Rin: <But I get the feeling that your dad is still just as kind as he was back then.>
Rin: <Which is why I think it's okay for you to tell him the truth.>
Mafuyu: Like back then...
Mafuyu's Father's Message: <Are you okay? This thunderstorm's massive.>
Mafuyu: ...
